	<center>
		<h1>Formulating a Query</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<p>
		A <strong>query</strong> expresses what you want to know in a form that is understood
		by whom or what you're asking.
	</p>
	<p>
		Queries can be expressed many formats
		<ul>
			<li>natural language</li>
			<li>boolean operations</li>
			<li>programatic creation</li>
			<li>...</li>
		</ul>
	</p>
